{\pard\sl-187\slmult0\par

{\pard\plain \li0\sl-298\slmult0 \ri0\nooverflow\qj{\f2\fs21 Little meaningful separation between the classes was extracted using this method. In some cases, the classes were farther apart from themselves than from other classes. In the cases where this was not true, the class separations are not generally signi cantly more distant than the intra-class distance. As such, this method was not deemed useful for the nal classi er.}\par}
}\sect\sbknone
\marglsxn5840\margrsxn5840\cols1\colno1\colw220
