{\pard\plain \li0\sl-297\slmult0 \ri0\nooverflow\qj\fi339 {\f2\fs22 Between the two-vector concatenation, and the three-vector concatenation, in general the two-vector concatenation performed better. The tall building class performed signi cantly worse in the three-vector, and the forest and highway classes performed very slightly worse. Overall, adding the gabor lter feature vectors did not seem to improve the results.}\par}
}\sect\sbknone
